channel.title: How to change your myspace URL -WORKS-
channel.description:
[b]If this is somehow against the rules. say So. I thought sharing my discovory world be helpful.[/b] When you first signup And choose your URL, it says that it never changeable. LIES!!!!! Send this message to the support system. This really works. But It does take them a month to reply to your message... So send this message to them
is there any way possibly to change my URL address. Because my parents want me to change it but i don't want to deal with having to send all those new friend requests and stuff, and i'm a leader of a group that i know soon will be like 25 people. so please could you make it happen some how?
This really works. So have fun with it i guess.
